Dead]] |network=[[PBS]]}}\n\n{{2008 Mumbai attacks}}\n{{Indo-Pakistani relations}}\n{{US War on Terror}}\n{{Mumbai topics}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mumbai Attacks}}\n[[Category:21st-century mass murder in India]]\n[[Category:2008 mass shootings]]\n[[Category:2008 Mumbai attacks| ]]\n[[Category:Explosions in 2008]]\n[[Category:Improvised explosive device bombings in India]]\n[[Category:Hostage taking in India]]\n[[Category:Spree shootings in India]]\n[[Category:Lashkar-e-Taiba attacks]]\n[[Category:Islam and antisemitism]]\n[[Category:Manmohan Singh administration]]\n[[Category:Terrorist incidents in India in 2008]]\n[[Category:Terrorist incidents in Mumbai]]\n[[Category:Mass murder in 2008]]\n[[Category:Mass murder in India]]\n[[Category:Mass shootings in India]]\n[[Category:Murder in Mumbai|2008]]\n[[Category:Israeli torture victims]]\n[[Category:Urban warfare]]\n[[Category:Terrorist incidents on railway systems]]\n[[Category:Mumbai Suburban Railway]]\n[[Category:Attacks on hotels in Asia]]\n[[Category:Islamic terrorist incidents in 2008]]\n[[Category:Islamic terrorism in India]]\n[[Category:November 2008 crimes]]\n[[Category:November 2008 events in Asia]]\n[[Category:Railway accidents and incidents in Maharashtra]]\n[[Category:Attacks on buildings and structures in India]]\n[[Category:2000s mass shootings in Asia]]\n[[Category:2000s in Mumbai]]\n", "text_old": "{{redirect|26/11|the date|November 26}}\n{{pp-pc1}}\n{{pp-move-indef}}\n{{short description|Terrorist attacks on Mumbai in 2008}}\n{{good article}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=July 2016}}\n{{Infobox civilian attack\n| title = 2008 Mumbai attacks\n| partof =\n| image = Bombaymapconfimed attacks.png\n| image_size = 250px\n| alt =\n| caption = Locations of the 2008 Mumbai attacks\n| map =\n| map_size =\n| map_alt =\n| map_caption =\n| location = [[Mumbai|Mumbai, India]]{{bulleted list |[[Leopold Caf\u00e9]]|[[Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj Terminus]]|[[The Ta